  "title": "Indoor Sales Support (Up to $4000 / Loyang)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Indoor Sales Support (ID1681)<br />Location: Loyang<br />Working Hours: Mon to Fri 9am – 6pm. (5.5 days work week with Saturday working from home if required)<br />Salary: $3000-$4000<br /><br />Job Responsibilities:<br />• Identify and pursue new sales opportunities through outbound calls, emails, and digital platforms.<br />• Respond to incoming inquiries and follow up on leads to convert prospects into customers.<br />• Develop and maintain strong relationships with new and existing clients.<br />• Prepare and present sales quotations & proposals<br />• Coordinate with internal departments to ensure timely order processing and customer satisfaction.<br />• Maintain and update CRM/database with accurate client and sales information.<br />• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets.<br />• Conduct market research to identify trends, competitors, and potential business growth areas.<br />• Provide after-sales support and resolve customer queries or issues promptly.<br />• Collaborate with the sales team on promotional campaigns and lead generation strategies.<br /><br />Job Requirements:<br />• Proven experience in sales, telesales, or business development<br />• Excellent communication, negotiation, and interpersonal skills.<br />• Strong customer service orientation.<br />• Proficient in MS Office and CRM software.<br />• Self-motivated, results-oriented, and a team player.<br />• Diploma/Degree in Business, Marketing, or related field preferred.<br />• Prior experience in Supply chain/Freight Forwarding is an advantage.</p>",
